<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
'''VRC+''', spoken as VRChat Plus, is a subscription service that provides users with additional features and benefits to enhance their VRChat experience. Purchasing VRC+ directly supports VRChat's development. VRC+ was officially released on [https://medium.com/vrchat/vrchat-plus-is-now-live-c8efdf796f2d December 3rd, 2020].
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
== Features ==
VRC+ offers various features that enhance the user experience:
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
===Increased avatar slots===
Supporters unlock more avatar slots and avatar lists.
