</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
===Inventory===
''See also [[Special:MyLanguage/Inventory|Inventory]] for more detailed information.''
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
Supporters unlock the ability to use and upload certain custom content types, which can be managed in the inventory. The content types include: User Icons, Photos, Custom Emoji, Custom Stickers and Prints. Users can create them by using the in-client [[Camera]], or through the VRChat website.
