<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
==== Sharing====
[[File:SharingPedestal.webp|thumb|200x200px|A sharing pedestal with a palette]]
[[Special:MyLanguage/Sharing|Sharing]] enables a VRC+ user to share custom emojis, custom stickers, photos, prints, and UI themes with other users. This allows a user to place a Sharing Pedestal in a world that other users can interact with. When a user leaves an instance, their pedestal will disappear. Sharing pedestals can be hidden by selecting it, blocking a user will also hide their pedestal.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
====Bundles====
[[File:Bundle August VRC+ Content Drop.png|thumb|120x120px|An image of a VRC+ content bundle]]
[[Special:MyLanguage/Inventory#Bundles_&_Packs|Bundles]] are a collection of content that users are able to claim for their Inventory, free for all users but some bundles can be exclusive to VRC+ supporters. These limited-time VRC+ only Inventory Bundles, when claimed, supporters are rewarded with exclusive inventory content. Usually bundles are available to claim for one month before a new bundle replaces it.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
=== Groups===
Supporters unlock the ability to create and join more [[Special:MyLanguage/Groups|groups]]. A VRC+ subscription is not required to retain ownership of a group once it has been created.
